-------------------------
1. Pre-handling of Datasets
	data_prepare (folder): the data form of the two datasets (i.e., RumourEval and PHEME)  conversion: json--> tsv. 
	The form of tsv: id,is_rumour,veracityLabel,for,against,observing,nones,category,text,reaction
	The results are saved to data (folder).
2.  Model Structure
src (folder): data_loader: data loading; model: the code of model; read_data_pheme: reading pheme data; train: the entrance of model training.
-------------------------